# Biggest architectural takeaway

Instead of mixing UI and business logic:

```
Old

removeProject()
    ↓
window.confirm()
    ↓
remove
```

Now:

```
Dropdown
     ↓
Open Dialog
     ↓
User confirms
     ↓
removeProject()
     ↓
Business logic
```

**UI decides whether the action should happen.**

**Business logic only performs the action.**

