This was my first end-to-end production issue where I:

* Reproduced a bug.
* Traced the execution flow.
* Understood component ownership.
* Read production React/TypeScript code.
* Implemented a UI change.
* Updated tests.
* Debugged multiple errors.
* Cleaned the Git diff.
